    "background": "本章中出现的商人，为主角提供消息",
    "character_arc": "",
    "dialogue_style": {
      "vocabulary_level": "现代白话",
      "patterns": ["爱用敬语"],
      "speech_habits": "客气圆滑"
    },
    "visual_prompt": "middle-aged male merchant, slightly overweight build, approximately 170cm. Round face with chubby cheeks, small shrewd eyes under thin arched brows, faint smile lines at corners. Warm tan skin, slightly oily sheen. Short black hair, neatly combed flat with minimal styling. Plain dark grey merchant robe with wide sleeves, worn brown leather belt, simple cloth shoes. Upright but relaxed posture, hands often clasped before him in a deferential gesture."
